Texts.Eng: A rather impressive painting. The blue undertones add a melancholy feel.
Texts.Chs: 一幅相当令人印象深刻的画。蓝色的底色增添了一种忧郁的感觉。

Texts.Eng: Ah, if only Apex cities could feel as peaceful as this one looks.
Texts.Chs: 啊，要是猿族的城市能像这座看起来那样平静就好了。

Texts.Eng: Ain't ever been much of a city slicker. This is one nice paintin' though.
Texts.Chs: 从来都不是一个精明的城市人。不过这是一幅不错的画。

Texts.Eng: An engaging painting of a busy city at night.
Texts.Chs: 这是一幅描绘夜晚繁忙城市的迷人画作。

Texts.Eng: Cities... Earth was chock full of 'em, once...
Texts.Chs: 城市。。。有一次，地球上到处都是。。。

Texts.Eng: Even after all this time, the site of a bustling city still awes me.
Texts.Chs: 即使过了这么久，这座繁华城市的所在地仍然令我敬畏。

Texts.Eng: Floran likes picture of city night life.
Texts.Chs: 叶族人喜欢城市夜生活的画面。

Texts.Eng: My homely little village could fit into just this picture a thousand times over.
Texts.Chs: 我那朴素的小村庄能与这张照片相配一千倍。
